ExampleCustomEvent
public abstract class CustomGameEvent extends GameEvent
An abstract class that allows for custom game events to be created. This class is used to create custom game events. You must extend this class to create a custom game event. This class is used to create the settings menu for the event and handle reading and writing.

To write to SQL override the GameEvent.getSQLData() method.
